The paper discusses a system for performing KB queries extended with analogical capabilities, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of distributional semantic vector space (DSVS) is also a key aspect of the paper, which falls under the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the limitations of commonsense knowledge bases, which is a topic in information retrieval (cs.IR) and computational complexity (cs.CC).
